ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#78: FILE: drivers/ata/libata-core.c:3802:
+		if ((rc = sata_scr_write(link, SCR_CONTROL, scontrol)))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

